3c8e049ad151650af38aa6cd102f41b96f953","tid":1330823,"uid":63350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"講撚左無一隻係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:36:23.000Z","msg":"我唔係叫大家原諒警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到依家都仲未辭職嘅都係仆街黎 <br />\n<br />\n我亦都唔期望佢地會良心發現 佢地只係一班利字當頭嘅狗 但正正因為咁 我地可以靠文宣煲大佢地比政府出賣緊 分化警隊同政府 如果做到 對我地係百利而無一害"},{"pid":"656a8d8bbe7baba5aa377de75c0c61e993d9f371","tid":1330823,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282f39abddeff22e88dc9d8350d791078e978819","tid":1330823,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3cea59bcf822af8c1840a3055ab8f98444375b","tid":1330823,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"傻啦,吠得幾大聲咪又係狗,有奶便是娘,咪又為份狗餅周圍咬<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係做麥記,你試下薪高糧準有無咁易劈炮?<br />\n<br />\n係廁所屌完老細咪又入番台底繼續含撚"}]}